title: Ep - 20 - Eden Sassoon of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills
description:
Eden Sassoon from Real Housewives of Beverly Hills discusses joining the show, addiction, and opening your life on reality television, Jarett Wieselman from Buzzfeed reviews Scientology the Aftermath and Seven Year Switch, and Kate’s friend Kevin (an orthopedic surgeon) rants about Vanderpump Rules and Summer House.
